modules.description: Tracks and records event-based data for performance analysis, supporting structured logging of timestamps, durations, and metadata. It processes and serializes data into JSON format, compatible with the Perfetto tracing viewer. Users can instrument applications to capture detailed execution flow and system events.

Provides a backend interface for interacting with a daemon, enabling trace logging with a unique identifier and configurable endpoint. Supports configuration through environment variables for trace activation, identifier, and connection address. Allows control over tracing behavior and communication with the daemon. Can be used to initialize and manage trace sessions in distributed systems.
